Fuschia_Text_Oldman_Text_0:
	.string "SAFARI ZONE has a zoo in front of the\n"
	.string "entrance. Out back is the SAFARI GAME\l"
	.string "for catching POKéMON.$"

Fuschia_Text_Kurt_Text_0:
	.string "KURT: Where's SHURA ? I said I'd meet\n"
	.string "her here.$"

Fuschia_Text_Youngster_Text_0:
	.string "That item ball in there is really a\n"
	.string "POKéMON.$"

Fuschia_Text_Bugcatcher_Text_0:
	.string "Did you try the SAFARI GAME? Some\n"
	.string "POKéMON can only be caught there.$"

Fuschia_Sign_Lapras_Text_0:
	.string "Name: LAPRAS\n"
	.string "A.K.A the king of the seas.$"

Fuschia_Sign_Kabuto_Text_0:
	.string "Name: KABUTO\n"
	.string "A POKéMON that was resurrected from a\l"
	.string "fossil.$"

Fuschia_Sign_Kangaskhan_Text_0:
	.string "Name: KANGASKHAN\n"
	.string "A maternal POKéMON that raises its\l"
	.string "young in a pouch on its belly.$"

Fuschia_Sign_Voltorb_Text_0:
	.string "Name: VOLTORB\n"
	.string "The very image of a POKéBALL.$"

Fuschia_Sign_Chansey_Text_0:
	.string "Name: CHANSEY\n"
	.string "Catching one is all up to chance.$"

Fuschia_Sign_Slowpoke_Text_0:
	.string "Name: SLOWPOKE\n"
	.string "Friendly and very slow moving.$"

Fuschia_Sign_FuchsiaSign_Text_0:
	.string "FUCHSIA CITY\n"
	.string "Behold! It's passion pink!$"

Fuschia_Sign_SafariZone_Text_0:
	.string "POKéMON Paradise\n"
	.string "Safari Zone$"

Fuschia_Text_Camper_Text_0:
	.string "It's the residential area of FUCHSIA\n"
	.string "CITY. I heard tourists are hosted here.$"

Fuschia_Sign_WardenHome_Text_0:
	.string "Safari Zone\n"
	.string "Warden's home$"

Fuschia_Sign_SafariGate_Text_0:
