	.string "POKéMON-u-Catch !$"

Fuschia_Text_Cooltrainer_Text_0:
	.string "I wonder if there are rare POKéMON in\n"
	.string "the SAFARI ZONE.\l"
	.string "Yes ?\p"
	.string "Well I'm going there right now !$"

Fuschia_Text_Man_Text_0:
	.string "KOGA our GYM LEADER left for his\n"
	.string "ancestors' home village. It's in JOHTO I\l"
	.string "think !$"

